track.name: Cousin Mary
comments: yeah...heart and soul...that's where trane meets you...
listen with your heart and soul
get going! get gooing ! allons y ! on ne sais pas ou aller , mais on y va tous
Listen with awe and enjoy your Lush Life.

first time listener-yes thats right-53 years old and hadnt heard anything by this gigantic legend-all i can say is-wow!!!!-i have really missed out-not at all what expected and quite a bit more. i have miles davis, basie, and later fusion on vinyl but not this. will listen  to some more-thanks for your time.
I flipping love this song. One of my all times to play as well.
You want Classic? You want Coltrane.

The heavyweight champion. He can sing like a bird and sting like a bee.
Whatever he plays is alright with me.
